title: Switch UI - Icon Pack v2.7 APK (Android)
description:
Soft corners embellished by the latest material palette. Switch is a set of beautiful icons carefully crafted for the current Android guidelines, in a unified fashion. Embrace the last icon pack you'll ever want to use and make the switch today.

FEATURES:
Includes 1300+ gorgeous icons.
27 HD wallpapers included.
Icon request tool. Premium requests available.
Quick-apply cards for numerous launchers.
Dynamic calendar support.
Constant updates & support.
SUPPORTED LAUNCHERS:
- Nova
- Apex
- Action
- Go
- ADW
- Most others that have icon pack support.

Recommended icon sizes:
Nova Launcher (Prime): 115%
Apex Launcher: 115%
Go Launcher: Big
Installation:
Icons can be applied directly from either the app itself or in your preferred launcher's theme settings.

What's in this version : (Updated : 6 April 2016)
- New set of Google Play icons.for details.
- 13 new icons.
Required Android O/S : 4.0.3+
